    COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[1] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[1]::DECIMAL ELSE NULL
    END, NULL), 0) AS dl_capacity, 
    COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[2] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[2]::DECIMAL ELSE NULL
    END, NULL), 0) AS ul_capacity,

    ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS linkuptime,

    ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS poweruptime,
    COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[13] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[13]::decimal
    ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS txpower,

    ELSE 0 END AS ramload,

    SELECT MIN(dt.created_at) as created_at, MAX(hi.sn) as sn, hi.nombre as item,
        CASE
            WHEN MAX(di.value)::text IS NULL THEN LAST(dt.value, dt.created_at)
            ELSE MAX(di.value)::text
        END as value
    FROM network.host_item as hi
    LEFT JOIN network.host as h ON h.id=hi.host_id AND h.empresa_id=hi.empresa_id
    LEFT JOIN estadistica.detalle_int AS di ON di.item_id=hi.id AND di.created_at>='${__from:date}'::timestamp AND di.created_at<='${__to:date}'::timestamp
    LEFT JOIN estadistica.detalle_text AS dt ON dt.item_id=hi.id AND dt.created_at>='${__from:date}'::timestamp AND dt.created_at<='${__to:date}'::timestamp
    WHERE h.ip='$ptmp'
        AND (
            hi.nombre='st-remote.hostname' OR hi.nombre='st-mac' OR hi.nombre='st-lastip' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.signal' OR hi.nombre='st-signal'
            OR hi.nombre='st-noisefloor' OR hi.nombre='st-airmax.dl_capacity' OR hi.nombre='st-airmax.ul_capacity' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.uptime'
            OR hi.nombre='st-uptime' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.tx_power' OR hi.nombre='st-distance' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.cpuload' 
            OR hi.nombre='st-remote.freeram' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.totalram' OR hi.nombre='st-remote.platform'
            OR hi.nombre='st-remote.version'
        )
    GROUP BY hi.nombre, hi.sn
    ORDER BY hi.sn ASC, hi.nombre ASC
) as q0
GROUP BY q0.sn

SELECT 
LOWER(COALESCE(q1.value[9]::text, NULL)) AS hostname, 
COALESCE(CASE WHEN q1.sn ~ '^([0-9a-fA-F]{2}:){5}[0-9a-fA-F]{2}$' THEN q1.sn::text ELSE NULL END, NULL) AS mac, 
COALESCE(NULLIF(q1.value[4]::text, ''), NULL) AS ip,
CONCAT(ROUND(COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[16] ~ '^-?[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[16]::decimal 
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0), 0), '/', 
ROUND(COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[11] ~ '^-?[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[11]::decimal 
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0), 0), ' dBm') AS signal,
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[6] ~ '^-?[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[6]::decimal 
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS noise,
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[1] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[1]::DECIMAL ELSE NULL
END, NULL), 0) AS dl_capacity, 
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[2] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[2]::DECIMAL ELSE NULL
END, NULL), 0) AS ul_capacity, 
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[17] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[17]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS linkuptime, 
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[14] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[14]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS poweruptime,
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[13] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[13]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS txpower, 
ROUND(COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[3] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[3]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) / 1000, 2) AS distance,
COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[7] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[7]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) AS cpuload, 
CASE 
WHEN COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE 
WHEN q1.value[12] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[12]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) > 0 THEN 
ROUND((COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[8] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[8]::decimal
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 0) * 100) / COALESCE(NULLIF(CASE WHEN q1.value[12] ~ '^[0-9]+(\.[0-9]+)?$' THEN q1.value[12]::decimal 
ELSE NULL END, NULL), 1), 2)
ELSE 0 END AS ramload,  
INITCAP(COALESCE(q1.value[10]::text, NULL)) AS modelo, 
CONCAT(
    SPLIT_PART(COALESCE(NULLIF(q1.value[15]::text, NULL), '0.0.0.0'), '.', 3), '.', 
    SPLIT_PART(COALESCE(NULLIF(q1.value[15]::text, NULL), '0.0.0.0'), '.', 4), '.', 
    SPLIT_PART(COALESCE(NULLIF(q1.value[15]::text, NULL), '0.0.0.0'), '.', 5)
) AS version
FROM (
    SELECT q0.sn, MIN(q0.created_at) AS created_at, array_agg(q0.value ORDER BY q0.item ASC) AS value
    FROM (
    SELECT MIN(dt.created_at) AS created_at, MAX(hi.sn) AS sn, hi.nombre AS item,
    CASE WHEN MAX(di.value)::text IS NULL THEN LAST(dt.value, dt.created_at)
    ELSE MAX(di.value)::text END AS value
    FROM network.host_item AS hi
    LEFT JOIN network.host AS h ON h.id = hi.host_id AND h.empresa_id = hi.empresa_id
    LEFT JOIN estadistica.detalle_int AS di ON di.item_id = hi.id AND di.created_at >= '${__from:date}'::timestamp AND di.created_at <= '${__to:date}'::timestamp
    LEFT JOIN estadistica.detalle_text AS dt ON dt.item_id = hi.id AND dt.created_at >= '${__from:date}'::timestamp AND dt.created_at <= '${__to:date}'::timestamp
    WHERE h.ip = '$ptmp' AND 
        (hi.nombre = 'st-remote.hostname' OR hi.nombre = 'st-mac' OR hi.nombre = 'st-lastip' 
        OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.signal' OR hi.nombre = 'st-signal' OR hi.nombre = 'st-noisefloor' 
        OR hi.nombre = 'st-airmax.dl_capacity' OR hi.nombre = 'st-airmax.ul_capacity' 
        OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.uptime' OR hi.nombre = 'st-uptime' OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.tx_power' 
        OR hi.nombre = 'st-distance' OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.cpuload' OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.freeram' 
        OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.totalram' OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.platform' OR hi.nombre = 'st-remote.version')
        GROUP BY hi.nombre, hi.sn
        ORDER BY hi.sn ASC, hi.nombre ASC) AS q0
    GROUP BY q0.sn
) AS q1;
